OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783698492
OL,3,CMan arrested after four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cseriously injured in alleged hit and
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FA 20-year-old man has been arrested
OL,8,Fafter a four-year-old boy was
OL,9,Fseriously injured in an alleged hit-
OL,10,Fand-run in South Shields.
OL,12,FThe man, who remains in custody, was
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of causing
OL,14,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police received a report
OL,17,Fthat a motorcycle had collided with a
OL,18,Fmother and child as they crossed the
OL,19,Froad outside Ocean Beach Pleasure
OL,20,FPark, on the seafront, shortly before
OL,21,F3.30pm on Saturday (27 June).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
