PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783698492
OL,3,CMan arrested after four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cseriously injured in alleged hit and
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FThe motorcycle ` described as a petrol-
OL,8,Fpowered motorbike intended for road
OL,9,Fuse but not displaying a registration
OL,10,Fplate ` was then reported to have left
OL,11,Fthe scene towards the Westoe Road area
OL,12,Fof the town, police said.
OL,14,FThe boy sustained serious injuries and
OL,15,Fwas taken to hospital, where he
OL,16,Fremains. The woman, aged in her 30s,
OL,17,Fsustained minor injuries and was also
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
