PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783698492
OL,3,CMan arrested after four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cseriously injured in alleged hit and
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FOfficers have recovered a motorcycle
OL,8,Fand helmet believed to be linked to
OL,9,Fthe incident, police said.
OL,11,FInvestigations are continuing, with
OL,12,Fpolice asking anyone with information,
OL,13,Fparticularly dashcam footage, to come
OL,14,Fforwards.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
